Title: Casio Mens Watch Protrek PRG-650-1ER
SPEC_Product Description: The PRG-650 is Tough Solar-powered, has a stainless steel bezel, Triple Sensor (altimeter/barometer, compass, thermometer), and STN LCD display. The index has a new design with more numerical indicators and there is now a Triple Sensor logo on the face. The PRG-650 is water-resistant to 100 meters and measures 51.6 x 51.5 x 13.4 mm like the PRG-600. Other features include world time (29 cities + UTC), 1/100 second stopwatch (24 hour with split), timer (60 minutes), 5 alarms, and double LED light.

Title: Casio Mens Watch G-Shock GA-110CB-1AER
